        "title": "기본",
        "html": "<cds-accordion alignment=\"END\" size=\"md\">\n  <cds-accordion-item title=\"Choose your plan\">\n    <p>\n      Compare plan features and select the option that best matches your\n      team's expected usage.\n    </p>\n  </cds-accordion-item>\n  <cds-accordion-item title=\"Add team members\">\n    <p>\n      Invite collaborators by email and assign their workspace roles\n      before launch.\n    </p>\n  </cds-accordion-item>\n  <cds-accordion-item title=\"Set payment details\">\n    <p>\n      Add billing information and choose whether to receive invoices by\n      email.\n    </p>\n  </cds-accordion-item>\n  <cds-accordion-item title=\"Review and confirm\">\n    <p>\n      Check your setup summary, then confirm to create the workspace for\n      your team.\n    </p>\n  </cds-accordion-item>\n</cds-accordion>",
        "react": "<Accordion\n  align=\"end\"\n  size=\"md\"\n>\n  <AccordionItem\n    onHeadingClick={function Kbe(){}}\n    title=\"Choose your plan\"\n  >\n    <p>\n      Compare plan features and select the option that best matches your team's\n      expected usage.\n    </p>\n  </AccordionItem>\n  <AccordionItem\n    onHeadingClick={function Kbe(){}}\n    title=\"Add team members\"\n  >\n    <p>\n      Invite collaborators by email and assign their workspace roles before launch.\n    </p>\n  </AccordionItem>\n  <AccordionItem\n    onHeadingClick={function Kbe(){}}\n    title=\"Set payment details\"\n  >\n    <p>\n      Add billing information and choose whether to receive invoices by email.\n    </p>\n  </AccordionItem>\n  <AccordionItem\n    onHeadingClick={function Kbe(){}}\n    title={<span>Review and confirm (<em>title can be a node</em>)</span>}\n  >\n    <p>\n      Check your setup summary, then confirm to create the workspace for your team.\n    </p>\n  </AccordionItem>\n</Accordion>",
        "vue": "<cv-accordion @change=\"onChange\" :align=\"align\" :size=\"size\">\n  <cv-accordion-item v-for=\"n in 4\" :key=\"`acc-item-${n}`\" :id=\"n % 2 ? `acc-item-${n}` : ''\" :disabled=\"disabledItems.has(n)\">\n    <template v-slot:title>Episode {{n}} </template>\n    <template v-slot:content>\n      <p>Did you hear that? They've shut down the main reactor. We'll be destroyed for sure. This is madness! We're doomed! There'll be no escape for the Princess this time. What's that? R2! R2-D2, where are you? At last! Where have you been? They're heading in this direction.</p>\n    </template>\n  </cv-accordion-item>\n</cv-accordion>\n<div><button @click=\"onToggleEpisode3\">Disable Episode 3</button></div>"
